									<div class="item ">
						<div class="item-wrapper">
															<a href="https://calmatters.org/blogs/events/2020/04/california-coronavirus-mental-health/" class="link thumb" aria-label="Read more about Watch: Taking care of your mental health during the pandemic">
									<div class="thumb-inner">
										<img width="321" height="214" src="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?fit=321%2C214" class="attachment-medium-wide-rec size-medium-wide-rec wp-post-image" alt="coronavirus mental health" srcset="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=2000 2000w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=300 300w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=768 768w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=1536 1536w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=460 460w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=321 321w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=780 780w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=858 858w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/covid-19-.jpg?w=794 794w" sizes="(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px" />									</div>
								</a>
							
															<p class="category">Breakdown: Mental Health</p>
																						<h2 class="title">Watch: Taking care of your mental health during the pandemic</h2>
													</div>
					</div>
									<div class="item ">
						<div class="item-wrapper">
